flowchart TD
    ADO[ADO Pipeline .ai/** change] --> BUS[Azure Service Bus]
    GH[GitHub Webhook] --> BUS
    POLL[Confluence Poller] --> BUS
    ADMIN[Admin Trigger] --> BUS

    BUS --> WRK[Index Worker]

    WRK --> FETCH[Fetch content via connector]
    FETCH --> CHUNK[Chunk content]
    CHUNK --> EMB[Generate embeddings]
    EMB --> COSMOS[Update Cosmos Vector Index]
    COSMOS --> INV[Invalidate cache]
    INV --> REDIS[Redis]
    INV --> BLOB[Blob]